HOW TO USE DATABASE API

examples down below.

145.24.222.221/recipe.php
145.24.222.221/recipe.php?id=5

145.24.222.221/login.php?user=user&pass=pass

145.24.222.221/register.php?user=bob&pass=water

145.24.222.221/search.php?input=pizza
145.24.222.221/search.php?input=chicken&category=pizza
145.24.222.221/search.php?input=&category=pizza         //<-- category search only

145.24.222.221/bookmark.php?user=user&add=5       //adds recept index 5
145.24.222.221/bookmark.php?user=user&remove=5    //removes recept index 5
145.24.222.221/bookmark.php?user=admin            //get data of specific user

145.24.222.221/rate.php?user=user&add=20&val=10  //adds rating to recipe number 20 (ratings between 0 and 10)
145.24.222.221/rate.php?user=user&remove=20 	    //removes rating of recipe number 20
145.24.222.221/rate.php?user=user 		        //returns ratings of specific user
145.24.222.221/rate.php?recipe=5 		        //returns average rating of recipe